OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774559156
OL,3,CAurigny CEO admits further losses and
OL,4,Cdoes not rule out public bailout
OL,6,FGuernsey's publicly owned airline
OL,7,Fremains in the red, two years after
OL,8,Fserious disruption derailed its
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,FIn 2024, Aurigny suffered a string of
OL,12,Fissues, including technical problems,
OL,13,Fstaffing shortages, and unusually high
OL,14,Fdisruption due to the weather.
OL,16,FIt ruined a run where the operator had
OL,17,Fbeen making a profit for the first
OL,18,Ftime in years, leading to a loss of
OL,19,F#6.5 million.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
