FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774559156
OL,3,CAurigny CEO admits further losses and
OL,4,Cdoes not rule out public bailout
OL,6,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,7,FChannel, the airline's Chief Executive
OL,8,FOfficer, Nico Bezuidenhout, has
OL,9,Frevealed that islanders should expect
OL,10,Fto see a loss once Aurigny's 2025
OL,11,Faccounts are published.
OL,13,FHe says: "The audit process is
OL,14,Fongoing, which should be done by May
OL,15,For June. It is a loss-making year.
OL,16,FIt's not as if on 31 December 2024 our
OL,17,Fdifficulties stopped. Losses that
OL,18,Fyou'll see, again, specifically relate
OL,19,Fto wet leasing."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774559156
OL,3,CAurigny CEO admits further losses and
OL,4,Cdoes not rule out public bailout
OL,6,FWet leasing is where an airline agrees
OL,7,Fto rent an aircraft from another
OL,8,Foperator with the full package needed
OL,9,Fto fly, including pilots, cabin crew,
OL,10,Finsurance and maintenance support.
OL,12,FThis comes at a high cost as Aurigny
OL,13,Falso faces fresh competition on
OL,14,Froutes, including British Airways
OL,15,Fstarting a Guernsey to London service,
OL,16,Fwhile Loganair has shown interest in
OL,17,Foperating flights from the Bailiwick
OL,18,Fto Southampton and Jersey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774559156
OL,3,CAurigny CEO admits further losses and
OL,4,Cdoes not rule out public bailout
OL,6,FThere has also been a reduction in the
OL,7,FGovernment subsidy to operate
OL,8,FAlderney's lifeline routes and Mr
OL,9,FBezeidenhout does not rule out the
OL,10,Fairline having to go back to the
OL,11,FStates for extra money if more
OL,12,Fservices are operated by other
OL,13,Fcompanies.
OL,15,FHe explains: "The market is finite and
OL,16,Fwhen you add a substantial load of
OL,17,Fcapacity into the market, it means
OL,18,Fthat when one seat is full, another is
OL,19,Fempty. That will have a commercial
OL,20,Fimpact on our business.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774559156
OL,3,CAurigny CEO admits further losses and
OL,4,Cdoes not rule out public bailout
OL,6,F"We will have to see what the
OL,7,Fimplication is of something like a
OL,8,Fcore route being impacted, like our
OL,9,FLondon route. What the implication of
OL,10,Fthat is and what the requirement is of
OL,11,Fthe business."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Aurigny says it is taking
OL,14,Fsteps to protect passengers from the
OL,15,Finflationary impacts of the Middle
OL,16,FEast conflict.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774559156
OL,3,CAurigny CEO admits further losses and
OL,4,Cdoes not rule out public bailout
OL,6,FThe cost of fuel has seen a huge jump
OL,7,Fin the last month as global oil supply
OL,8,Fis impacted and while the airline
OL,9,Fstates it is working hard to shield
OL,10,Fcustomers from price hikes, it admits
OL,11,Fsome difficult decisions have had to
OL,12,Fbe made.
OL,14,FThis includes cancelling certain
OL,15,Fflights between mid-April and June,
OL,16,Fcombining services from nearby UK
OL,17,Fairports to reduce the number of empty
OL,18,Fseats, and the introduction of a
OL,19,Ftemporary fuel surcharge of #2 on all
OL,20,Fbookings made from 20 March.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774559156
OL,3,CAurigny CEO admits further losses and
OL,4,Cdoes not rule out public bailout
OL,6,FPhilip Saunders, Chief Commercial
OL,7,FOfficer at Aurigny, adds in a
OL,8,Fstatement: "Unfortunately, we have to
OL,9,Fpass on some of the resulting costs to
OL,10,Fcustomers to ensure sustainable air
OL,11,Fservices to and from Guernsey.
OL,13,F"While a small island community, we
OL,14,Fare not immune from the realities
OL,15,Fpresented by the global travel
OL,16,Fecosystem."
OL,18,FOn average, Aurigny says fuel costs
OL,19,Frepresent almost a third of its costs
OL,20,Fand bookings for May are 13% down
OL,21,Fcompared to last year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774559156
OL,3,CAurigny CEO admits further losses and
OL,4,Cdoes not rule out public bailout
OL,6,FHowever, the airline hopes to have a
OL,7,Fstrong summer season as prospective UK
OL,8,Fand European holidaymakers look closer
OL,9,Fto home due to the global uncertainty.
OL,11,FAurigny route changes between mid-
OL,12,FApril and early June:
OL,14,FThe airline is in the process of
OL,15,Freplacing its aircraft, moving away
OL,16,Ffrom the Dornier to the Twin Otter.
OL,18,FThis transitional period has seen an
OL,19,Funusually high number of cancelled
OL,20,Fflights since the beginning of the
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774559156
OL,3,CAurigny CEO admits further losses and
OL,4,Cdoes not rule out public bailout
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Channel after hundreds
OL,7,Fof people protested at Alderney
OL,8,FAirport to demand a better service, Mr
OL,9,FBezeidenhout says the disruption is
OL,10,Fmainly due to unprecedented weather
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,FHe explains: "The weather has been
OL,14,Fmaterial this year ... that impact has
OL,15,Fbeen acute.
OL,17,F"This year, 137 flights to and from
OL,18,FAlderney were cancelled specifically
OL,19,Fdue to the weather, where a year ago
OL,20,Fit was close to a quarter of that
OL,21,Ffigure."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
